-- NTPC Trading Unit Chief Goyal Resigns, Leaving Indian Solar Power Program
-- B y   N a t a l i e   O b i k o   P e a r s o n
-- 2010-12-01T05:26:31Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-01/ntpc-trading-unit-chief-goyal-resigns-leaving-indian-solar-power-program.html
NTPC Ltd.’s trading unit’s Chief
Executive Officer A.K. Goyal resigned from his position
yesterday, he said in a phone interview from New Delhi today.  Goyal headed NTPC Vidyut Vyapar Nigam Ltd., which is
overseeing bidding for solar projects under India’s national
solar mission.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Natalie Obiko Pearson in Mumbai at 
